sequenceDiagram
  box rgba(239, 246, 255, 0.65) Presentation Layer
    actor U as Admin/User
    participant UI as Transactions UI
  end

  box rgba(236, 253, 245, 0.65) Application/API Layer
    participant API as Worker Transactions API
    participant AUTH as Auth/RBAC
    participant SCOPE as Tenant Scope
    participant TXSVC as Transaction Service
    participant INVSVC as Inventory Sync Service
  end

  box rgba(245, 243, 255, 0.65) Data Layer
    participant DB as D1 business tables
    participant AUD as audit_log
  end

  U->>UI: Nhập transaction và line items
  UI->>API: POST /api/transactions
  API->>AUTH: Verify session and EDIT_TRANSACTIONS
  AUTH-->>API: authorized
  API->>SCOPE: Resolve tenant/company scope
  SCOPE-->>API: tenantId companyId
  Note over SCOPE,DB: All references are validated inside the resolved tenant/company scope.
  API->>TXSVC: Validate payload
  TXSVC->>DB: Validate part warehouse project market contact
  DB-->>TXSVC: valid refs
  TXSVC->>TXSVC: Prepare header and active line items
  TXSVC->>INVSVC: Build sync plan by movement_type
  INVSVC->>DB: Check stock for Sale Redeploy Recycle

  alt Insufficient stock
    DB-->>INVSVC: available < requested
    INVSVC-->>API: INSUFFICIENT_STOCK
    API-->>UI: 409 no partial write
  else Enough stock or Purchase
    INVSVC->>DB: Prepare inventory updates and movements
    TXSVC->>DB: D1 batch transaction items inventory movements
    TXSVC->>AUD: INSERT TRANSACTION_CREATE and INVENTORY_MOVE_AUTO
    API-->>UI: 201 transaction id inventorySyncStatus
    UI->>API: GET scoped list/summary
    API->>DB: SELECT transactions/dashboard data in scope
    DB-->>API: updated list/summary
    API-->>UI: refreshed data
  end

  opt Missing warehouse or part for sync
    TXSVC->>DB: INSERT transaction and items only
    TXSVC->>AUD: INSERT TRANSACTION_CREATE
    API-->>UI: 201 inventorySyncStatus not_ready
  end

  alt Cross-scope reference
    TXSVC-->>API: 400/404 invalid reference
    API-->>UI: error no write
  else Invalid movement or quantity
    TXSVC-->>API: 400 validation error
    API-->>UI: validation error
  end
